<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title
      >{{name}}, welcome to the Bible Journey Challenge - Payment and Activation
      Instructions</mj-title
    >
    <mj-font
      name="Open Sans"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,600,800"
    />
    <mj-font
      name="Raleway"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@600&display=swap"
    />

    <mj-style inline="inline">
      .bibleplan-border-radius { -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0,
      0.25); -moz-box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); box-shadow: 0px
      4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); -webkit-border-radius: 6px;
      -moz-border-radius: 6px; border-radius: 6px; }
      .bibleplan-text-align-center { text-align: center; }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#fcfaf5">
    <mj-spacer height="80px" />

    <mj-wrapper border-radius="6px" padding="0">
      <mj-section
        background-color="#6A2D56"
        padding="40px 0"
        border-top="1px solid #6A2D56"
        border-right="1px solid #6A2D56"
        border-left="1px solid #6A2D56"
      >
        <mj-column>
          <mj-image
            src="https://bibleplan844507025.files.wordpress.com/2024/01/bible-journey-logo.png"
            alt="Example image"
            width="150px"
          />
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section
        background-color="#ffffff"
        border-radius="0 0 6px 6px"
        border-bottom="1px solid #d5dadf"
        border-right="1px solid #d5dadf"
        border-left="1px solid #d5dadf"
      >
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Raleway, Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="22px"
          >
            Hello, {{name}}!
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            We are pleased to have you with us on the Bible Journey Challenges!
            We are looking forward to helping you embark on this journey of
            faith and knowledge.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Raleway, Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="18px"
          >
            Step 1: Make Your Payment
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            To start, access our payment system by clicking the link below:
            <a
              style="color: #6a2d56"
              href="https://buy.stripe.com/28obLYfOi6updpe6oo"
            >
              Stripe Payment Link.
            </a>
            This process is safe and your information will be protected.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Raleway, Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="18px"
          >
            Step 2: Confirm Your Payment
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            After completing the payment, please confirm it by contacting us.
            You can do this through our email or WhatsApp. Your confirmation is
            important so we can verify the payment and activate your access to
            the plan.
            <a style="color: #6a2d56" href="https://wa.me/5511958079381">
              Click here to send a message via WhatsApp </a
            >.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Raleway, Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="18px"
          >
            Step 3: Access the Plan
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            Once your payment is confirmed, we will activate your access to the
            paid plan of Bible Journey. You will be able to start using the app
            and begin the challenge immediately!
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Raleway, Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="18px"
          >
            We Are Here to Help
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            If you have any questions or need assistance, contact us via
            WhatsApp or email. Our goal is that you have an amazing experience
            with the app.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            Thank you for choosing Bible Journey. We are excited to follow your
            growth and engagement in this journey!
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            Sincerely,
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text
            font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
            font-size="16px"
            line-height="23px"
          >
            The Bible Journey Team
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
    </mj-wrapper>

    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-family="Open-Sans, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          line-height="23px"
        >
          <div style="text-align: center">Â© Bible Journey</div>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-social font-size="15px" icon-size="30px" mode="horizontal">
          <mj-social-element
            background-color="#6A2D56"
            name="instagram"
            href="https://www.instagram.com/usebiblejourney/"
          >
          </mj-social-element>
        </mj-social>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
